contentrichtext.text: '''WSPA''' may refer to: *[[World Society for the Protection of Animals]], an international non-profit animal welfare organisation *[[Western States Petroleum Association]] *[[World Student Press Agency]], a Canadian student news agency *[[Winston-Salem Preparatory Academy]], a public school in Forsyth County, North Carolina, United States *[[WSPA-TV]], a television station (channel 7 digital) licensed to Spartanburg, South Carolina, United States *[[WSPA-FM]], a radio station (98.9 FM) licensed to Spartanburg, South Carolina, United States *[[WOLI (AM)]], a radio station (910 AM) licensed to Spartanburg, South Carolina, United States, which used the call sign WSPA prior to October 2005 {{disambig}} [[Category:Broadcast call sign disambiguation pages]]
